OL,3,CFM 'delighted' over PM's U-turn on
OL,4,Ccuts to winter fuel payments
OL,6,FThe prime minister's official
OL,7,Fspokesman said Starmer wanted the
OL,8,Fchanges to be introduced "as quickly
OL,9,Fas possible", as ITV News Political
OL,10,FCorrespondent Carl Dinnen explains
OL,12,FThe First Minister has said she is
OL,13,F'delighted' after the Prime Minister
OL,14,Fconfirmed the UK Government is
OL,15,Frethinking the controversial cuts to
OL,16,Fwinter fuel payments for pensioners.
OL,18,FThe Prime Minister said that "as the
OL,19,Feconomy improves" he wanted to look at
OL,20,Fwidening eligibility for the payments
OL,21,Fworth up to #300.
