OL,3,CFM 'delighted' over PM's U-turn on
OL,4,Ccuts to winter fuel payments
OL,6,F"The cuts to the Winter Fuel Payment
OL,7,Fcaused real concern to people across
OL,8,FWales.
OL,10,F"We are yet to hear the details of the
OL,11,Fannouncement, but I'm hopeful that
OL,12,Fsignificantly more people will now
OL,13,Fbenefit from the payment."
OL,15,FThe decision to means-test the
OL,16,Fpreviously universal payment was one
OL,17,Fof the first announcements by
OL,18,FChancellor Rachel Reeves after
OL,19,FLabour's landslide election victory
OL,20,Flast year and has been widely blamed
OL,21,Ffor the party's collapse in support.
