OL,3,CFM 'delighted' over PM's U-turn on
OL,4,Ccuts to winter fuel payments
OL,6,FThe Government insisted the policy was
OL,7,Fnecessary to help stabilise the public
OL,8,Ffinances, allowing the improvements in
OL,9,Fthe economic picture which Sir Keir
OL,10,Fsaid could result in the partial
OL,11,Freversal of the measure.
OL,13,FHe said he understood the financial
OL,14,Fpressures on pensioners as he made the
OL,15,Fannouncement at Prime Minister's
OL,16,FQuestions.
OL,18,F"I recognise that people are still
OL,19,Ffeeling the pressure of the cost-of-
OL,20,Fliving crisis, including pensioners,"
OL,21,FSir Keir told the Commons.
