OL,3,CFM 'delighted' over PM's U-turn on
OL,4,Ccuts to winter fuel payments
OL,6,F"As the economy improves, we want to
OL,7,Fmake sure people feel those
OL,8,Fimprovements in their days as their
OL,9,Flives go forward. That is why we want
OL,10,Fto ensure that, as we go forward, more
OL,11,Fpensioners are eligible for winter
OL,12,Ffuel payments."
OL,14,FHe said the Government will "only make
OL,15,Fdecisions we can afford" and will
OL,16,Ftherefore look at this as part of a
OL,17,F"fiscal event" ` indicating a change
OL,18,Fwill not be announced before the
OL,19,FChancellor's autumn budget.
